  GasketMomentFactor.xml
  ======================
  Moment Factor F_M for ASME VIII-1 UG-44 nozzle external-load check.

  Two data sets are provided:
    Table id="UG-44-1"   – per-NPS values derived from ASME VIII-1 Table UG-44-1
    CodeCase id="2901-1" – per-NPS values per ASME Code Case 2901-1
                           (supersedes Table UG-44-1 when the Code Case is invoked)

  Both sections share identical XML structure:
    <Standard id="B16.5 | B16.47">
      <Size NPS="..." DN="...">
        <Rating class="150|300|600|900|1500|2500" FM="..." />
      </Size>
    </Standard>
  For B16.47, <Size> elements are nested inside <Series id="A|B">.

  Scope: <Rating> elements are omitted for class/size combinations outside scope
  of the applicable table or code case.

  Notes:
    B16.47 Series B, Table UG-44-1:
      Classes 150/300 for NPS 26-46: FM = 0.1 + (48 - NPS) / 56  (pre-computed below)
      Classes 600/900 for NPS 26-46: FM = 0.13
      NPS 48-60:  Class 150 = 0.10; Class 300 = 0.10, except NPS 60 = 0.03
-->
